.cs 3 on
.item 'UNLEARN Command' 'Added on 06/28/84 by LSO'
.boxon
UNLEARN word
.*      <-->
.* FIELD COMMAND HELP UNLEARN word
.boxoff

.* DESCRIPTION
The UNLEARN command allows you to remove a word from your private spelling
dictionary.  Type HELP LEARN for a description of how to add words to your
private spelling dictionary.

.* SELECT 'UNLEARN Command Options'
.us Option Description

.* OPTION WORD
.optix word
word\\\\\\\\\\\\specifies a word that is to be removed from your private
                spelling dictionary.
.cs 3 off
